Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉…莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:29.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來很睏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:27.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以剛才一直在打瞌睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和姊姊一直看DVD到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼的DVD？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人真是的 一直都迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為我有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:01.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒發燒 但是覺得你腦子好像不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂下診斷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 昨天怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃來接你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還打扮過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來兩個人還坐了纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,纜車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊說想看遠方 所以去了瞭望臺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:22.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這算是約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直悶在家裡 所以想轉換一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還是淋雨了 就去了便利商店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 明明是下雨天還特地去坐纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去買毛巾…毛巾…和姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:54.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,買毛巾 毛巾… 姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰去叫一下老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃 蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不要緊了 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來像沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是有點頭暈 你小題大做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才連話都不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把毛巾弄乾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:46.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的只是有點頭暈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:01.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看弟弟的臉不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難看的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說這什麼呢 我們不是有血肉相連的姊弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說這話就等於在說自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臉才不難看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:24.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不難受了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上我們吃了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:37.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在家裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:40.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後說一起看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三部恐怖片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得 自己很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得一直很不清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:02.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我們昨天回來的時候有沒有遇見什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:06.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的什麼人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像忘記了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 今天就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:19.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,身體情況的確不好 我帶他去房間裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,扶他去房間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:49.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這…樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下次晴天的時候再一起出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:25.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在晴天看到的藍天又會有不同的顏色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 正在回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友聊了會兒 所以回家稍晚了些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果不走遠點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,休息過了所以不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我已經沒事了 你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放著傷者不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是被救的孩子不要任性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,互相幫助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去醫院真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你的灼傷才是 不去不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真不小心 也不帶傘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為雨突然停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不疼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那你還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一個人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂 那樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:36.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你不問我從哪裡來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:49.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要我問比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,隱瞞的事情沒必要特地去問對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:02.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 你是夜禍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這點小傷不能治癒好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我破壞了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被刺也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,門鎖著還真是少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的情況還是很糟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是好天氣 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:51.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:53.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃 依人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人的情況怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下的話馬上就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:03.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:07.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 請保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃看起來很累的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:24.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:30.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉又在我的夢裡出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我刺傷了茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不可能有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:47.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為依人忘不了茉莉 所以才會做這種夢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點忘記她的話 永遠都會痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮同學今天休息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說因為感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:30.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名每天都去接他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都這樣了還說沒有和森宮同學在交往 真名真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 森宮同學也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 總覺得有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:59.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,起來得太早了 睡了個回籠覺 又睡著了第三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,話說有一個大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大衝擊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是和鬍子紳士在一起的那個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鬍子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是在哪裡拍到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天回家時在電車上偶然看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個孩子的媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他們嘴裡的YACA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,瞞著鬍子紳士去見小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,複雜的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:38.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不會又是沒有根據的胡思亂想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這種事呢 看她們的表情就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉她還在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,紗繪 把這張照片發到我的手機上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟老師說我肚子痛 頭痛 腰痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真名是這件感情糾紛的關聯者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎？ 有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:25.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢？ 依人他起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我見見他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:44.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 茉莉她還在 就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 這裡有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:50.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:52.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:54.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:55.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那請你馬上告訴依人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她是依人重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不告訴依人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:15.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃 蒼乃 蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:26.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃 蒼乃 蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:06.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依…人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
