Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:41.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:44.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:01.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:09.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:16.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快恢復原樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不在了 茉莉已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:23.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 是我弄髒了依人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓依人痛苦的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為好不容易可以得到幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想和依人在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:41.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在依人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在依人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有依人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們重頭來過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不再讓依人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:11.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一切結束後 兩個人再一起安靜地生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉已經不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:46.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃不讓進正門 那我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:58.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉已經不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是…可是這是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉已經不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛一個人胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:44.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說依人 你知道地點在哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可以在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小依叫真名的時候要叫真名小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小依看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊她用手刀把圍住她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:43.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,強…強壯的男孩子們給…
